Hello. I have downloaded roller sourcecode, and I am trying to run its 
build. The build starts the junit tests, but for some reason most of the 
tests fail. I have managed to make them run before from another build, 
but it doesn't say why the tests fail.
Is there a way to view the compiler outputs? Or Junit compiler output?
All I get now is  [junit] 2006-04-21 13:13:43,428 WARN 
org.roller.config.RollerConfig - failed

And this does'nt say much to me.
